{"tid":2331961,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"萬八蚊LG Rollable 新機規格細節首度曝光","createTime":"2020-12-19T08:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T12:06:55.000Z","uid":64745,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"edc8e430c7d04b769b052102ccdf73694272ff30","tid":2331961,"uid":64745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:30:43.000Z","msg":"柔性螢幕技術開始成熟，手機品牌亦嘗試探索不同機身設計，去發掘柔性螢幕的各種可能性。一直有傳 LG 會以捲軸式技術，將部份螢幕於不需要使用時收起，到需要時則拉開，而這款名為 LG Rollable 的手機最近有新消息在網上流傳。 &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n根據爆料者的說法，LG Rollable 配備一塊 7.4 吋捲軸式柔性螢幕，手機模式的解像度為 2,428 x 1,080（20 : 9），在影片模式則為 2,428 x 1,366（16 : 9），至於平板模式的解像度為 2,428 x 1,600（3 : 2）。 消息指 LG 已經敲定 Rollable 會採用 Qualcomm Snapdragon 888 處理器，搭配 16GB RAM 和內置 4,200mAh 電池。 &nbsp;   早前的傳聞指 LG Rollable 會在 2021 年上半年發表，當中 3 月的可能性較高，但亦有可能會延期至 6 月。有爆料者昨日表示，LG Rollable 的美元定價為 2,359 美元（折合 HK$18,288），較 Samsung Galaxy Z Fold2 的 HK$16,998 和 Huawei Mate Xs 5G 的 HK$17,888 上市定價還要貴。<br />\n<br />\nsource : <a href=\"https://www.phonearena.com/news/lg-rollable-phone-specs-and-price-leaked_id129126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.phonearena.com%2Fnews%2Flg-rollable-phone-specs-and-price-leaked_id129126&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBbTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=71cae7d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.phonearena.com/news/lg-rollable-phone-specs-and-price-leaked_id129126</a>"},{"pid":"7345239458376e88eb2c53e7ab2fde19fed52386","tid":2331961,"uid":367723,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"仲以為oppo自己諗個idea<br />\n原來又係抄人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c4adc798fa6158474f7406ad03e9d663487d76","tid":2331961,"uid":64745,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7345239458376e88eb2c53e7ab2fde19fed52386","tid":2331961,"uid":367723,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"仲以為oppo自己諗個idea<br />\n原來又係抄人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cite